query:
SELECT r.id, r.name, COUNT(rw.id) as waypoint_count 
FROM routes r 
LEFT JOIN route_waypoints rw ON r.id = rw.routeId 
WHERE rw.address NOT LIKE '%City, State%' 
GROUP BY r.id 
LIMIT 5
